response.overview: Five friends head out to rural Texas to visit the grave of a grandfather. On the way they stumble across what appears to be a deserted house, only to discover something sinister within. Something armed with a chainsaw.
response.tagline: Who will survive and what will be left of them?
response.title: The Texas Chain Saw Massacre
